column5: went out in my own boat 1st trip sat. sited 5 muskies no takers ran into big cliff.. he had cpl eyes toured various areas lake...lost a few went back to 1st spot around 1pm the bite was on..10 min 3 walleye landed.. lost 3more....all over slot size  21" + a good day out !
Awesome! The eyes were on fire this weekend on the Trent river too..Havent had a better time, Walleye fishing in years...
A good day for sure, seems as if the bite for any species was good this weekend.
